00:13:12.040 --> 00:13:16.500
&gt;&gt; The Battle of the Black
Sea, or as the Somalis call it,

00:13:16.500 --> 00:13:19.720
Maalintii Rangers, the
Day of the Rangers,

00:13:19.720 --> 00:13:23.270
is one that America has
preferred to forget.

00:13:23.270 --> 00:13:26.360
The images it produced of dead
soldiers dragged by jeering mobs

00:13:26.360 --> 00:13:32.850
through the streets of Mogadishu
are among the most horrible

00:13:32.850 --> 00:13:41.270 position:56%
and disturbing in our history, made
all the worse by the good intentions

00:13:41.270 --> 00:13:43.990
that prompted our intervention.

00:13:43.990 --> 00:13:49.740
There were no American reporters
in Mogadishu on October third

00:13:49.740 --> 00:14:05.570
and fourth of 1993, but after a
week or so of frenzied attention,

00:14:05.570 --> 00:14:10.850
the world events quickly
summoned journalists elsewhere.

00:14:10.850 --> 00:14:17.190
President Clinton's decision,
just days after the fight,

00:14:17.190 --> 00:14:19.680
to end Task Force Ranger's
mission to Somalia,

00:14:19.680 --> 00:14:24.710
accomplished what he intended,
to slam the door on the episode.

00:14:24.710 --> 00:14:27.590 position:56%
In Washington, a whiff of failure is
enough to induce widespread amnesia.

00:14:27.590 --> 00:14:28.890
There was a [inaudible]
investigation and two days

00:14:28.890 --> 00:14:30.190
of congressional hearings

00:14:30.190 --> 00:14:31.490
that produced the partisan report
blaming the president and Secretary

00:14:31.490 --> 00:14:32.790
of Defense Les Aspin, who
resigned two months later.

00:14:32.790 --> 00:14:34.090
But that was it.

00:14:34.090 --> 00:14:35.390
I began working on this story
about two and a half years

00:14:35.390 --> 00:14:36.690
after the battle was fought.

00:14:36.690 --> 00:14:37.990
I've been intrigued by the
early accounts of the fight,

00:14:37.990 --> 00:14:39.290
both as a citizen and as a writer.

00:14:39.290 --> 00:14:40.590
But the undertaking intimidated me.

00:14:40.590 --> 00:14:41.890
I had no military background
or sources.

00:14:41.890 --> 00:14:43.190
Nevertheless, I remained
curious enough

00:14:43.190 --> 00:14:44.490
