journalism that's going on

00:43:39.770 --> 00:43:41.610
and people risking their
lives to tell stories

00:43:41.610 --> 00:43:43.300
in super complicated places.

00:43:43.300 --> 00:43:46.730
And I don't want to say
that that's not happening.

00:43:46.730 --> 00:43:50.940
But at the same time, there's young
people all over the place trying

00:43:50.940 --> 00:43:54.510
to figure out how to chase
dreams like Sa'ad and Saadiq.

00:43:54.510 --> 00:43:57.830
And if we think about what
bullying looks like, you know,

00:43:57.830 --> 00:44:02.760
if the whole world looks to
you in a light that feels

00:44:02.760 --> 00:44:06.760
like fear, what does that mean?

00:44:06.760 --> 00:44:08.060
There's social media now.

00:44:08.060 --> 00:44:09.450
That's how these kids communicate.

00:44:09.450 --> 00:44:10.750
They know how the world
looks at them.

00:44:10.750 --> 00:44:12.050
How do you take that on?

00:44:12.050 --> 00:44:15.240
They have passports that can't
be, it's a license to go nowhere.

00:44:15.240 --> 00:44:16.540
Like they literally cannot travel.

00:44:16.540 --> 00:44:18.930
No one's going to take
a Somali passport.

00:44:18.930 --> 00:44:21.420
They can maybe go to Turkey, maybe.

00:44:21.420 --> 00:44:27.180
So, Sa'ad and Saadiq, for me, and
I hope for a lot of other people,

00:44:27.180 --> 00:44:30.160
and an entire generation
back in Somalia represent

00:44:30.160 --> 00:44:34.390
that if you do the best that
you can with the situation

00:44:34.390 --> 00:44:39.070
that you're given, you never know
when your shot to get your dream

00:44:39.070 --> 00:44:40.820
to come true will happen.

00:44:40.820 --> 00:44:43.960
And I think the fact that they
chose education, they chose to try

00:44:43.960 --> 00:44:47.230
to play soccer, I hope
that that empowers a bunch

00:44:47.230 --> 00:44:51.370
of young people back in Mogadishu
and, frankly, who are Somalis

00:44:51.370 --> 00:44:54.240
and immigrants and anybody that's
trying to chase their dreams

00:44:54.240 --> 00:44:56.020
in different parts of the world.

